hadiths[16]{hadithnumber,text}:
4138,"Hazrat Yazid bin Hurmuz sey riwayat hai ke Najda Haroori (Khaariji) jab Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki shorish (vidroh) key doran mein aaya to usney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham nama bheja aur puchha ke aap ki raey mein (Khums mein sey) qurbat daaron ka hissa kisey milega? unhoney farmaya : hamein, yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key rishtey-daaron ko. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye hissa un (bani Haashim aur bani Muttlib) key liye taqseem kiya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi hamein (khums mein sey) kuchh maal pesh kiya jisey hamney apney haq sey kam samjha to hamney usey qubul karney sey inkar kar diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein pesh kaash! ki thi ke wo un mein sey nikah karney waley ki madad kerengey. unkey maqrooz ka qarz ada kerengey aur un sey mohtaj logon ko atiyaat dengey. is sey zayed deney sey unhoney inkar kar diya."
4139,"Hazrat Yazid bin Hurmuz sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Najda Haroori ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey tahreeri taur par puchha ke qurbat-daari ka hissa kis ko milega? Yazid bin Hurmuz ney kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf sey Najda ko jawab mainey tehreer kiya tha. mainey likha tha ke tum ney mujh sey qurbat-daaron key hissey key mutalliq puchha hai ke kis ko milega? ye hissa darasal hum ehale-bait ka hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein ye pesh kaash! ki thi ke is hissey mein sey main, tum mein sey ghair-shaadi-shuda ki shaadi karunga aur faqir (gharib) ko Atiya dunga aur maqrooz ka qarz ada karunga, lekin hamney (isey qubul karney sey) inkar kar diya isleye ke wo hamara khums purey ka pura hamein dey dein. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney is sey inkar kiya to hamney ye unhi par chhod diya (aur thoda leney sey inkar kar diya)."
4140,"Hazrat Auzai sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney umr bin Waleed ko likha ke terey baap (Waleed bin Abdul-Malik bin Marwan) ney tujhey pura khums dey diya tha, halanke dar-haqiqat terey baap ka hissa eik aam musalman key hissey key barabar tha. us (khums) main to Allah Taala ka haq tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbat-daaron ka, yatimon aur miskinon aur musafiron ka haq tha. qiyamat key din terey baap sey jhagda karney waley log kis qadr hongey ! wo shakhs kaisey najat paeyga jis sey haq wasul karney waley is qadr ziyada hon? phir tera elaniya aalaate-mausiqi (sangeet) istimal karna aur bansuri bajana Islam key andar eik bid'at hai. mera irada hai ke main terey paas aisa shakhs bhejun jo terey lambey lambey qabeeh baalon ko kaat dey (ya terey lambey qabeeh baalon sey pakad kar tujhey ghaseet laye)."
4141,Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main aur Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. hamara maqsad aap sey ghazwae-Hunain ki ghanimat banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib mein taqseem karney key barey mein baat cheet karna tha. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney hamarey bhaiyon banu Muttalib bin Abd Munaaf ko (khums mein sey) hissa diya magar hamein kuchh nahin diya jabkey aap sey hamari aur un ki rishtey-daari eik jaisi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib ko eik hi chiz samajhta hun. Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney banu Abd Shams aur Banu-Nofal ko us khums mein sey kuchh nahin diya jaisey aap ney banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib ko hissa diya.
4142,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbat-daari ka hissa banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib mein taqseem farma diya to main aur Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! banu Haashim ki fazilat ka to hum inkar nahin kartey kyonkey wo aap ka khandan hai, Allah Taala ney aap ko un mein sey banaya hai lekin banu Muttalib ko aap ney diya aur hamein nahin diya, halanke dar-haqiqat aap sey hamara aur unka talluq eik jaisa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo daure-jahiliyat mein bhi mujh sey juda nahin rahey aur Islam mein bhi hamarey sath rahey, lihaza banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib eik chiz hain. (ye farmatey huye) aap ney apney dono haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusrey mein phansaya."
4143,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwae-Hunain key din eik oont key pehlu sey oon ka eik baal liya aur farmaya : aey logo ! Allah Taala ney jo kuchh tumhen ata farmaya hai, is mein sey merey liye khums key ilawa itna bhi jayez nahin aur khums bhi phir tum par hi lota diya jata hai. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke (Hadees key raawi) Abu-Salaam ka naam Mamtur hai aur wo Habshi hai. aur (Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi Abu-Umama ka naam Sudayyi bin Ajlaan hai."
4144,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik oont key paas aaye aur apni do ungliyon key darmiyan uskey kohaan sey oon pakdi, aur farmaya : merey liye maale-ghanimat sey itna bhi jayez nahin ilawa khums key aur wo khums bhi tum par hi lota diya jata hai."
4145,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke banu Nazeer ka maal un maalon mein sey tha jo Allah Taala ney apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jang key baghair ata farmaya tha, musalmanon ney uskey husool key liye is par apney ghodey aur oont nahin dodaye they (ladaai key baghair hi hasil huwa). aap is mein sey apney liye (aur apney ghar walon key liye) eik saal ki khurak rakh letey they aur baqi maal ko jihad Fi-sabililah ki tayyari key liye ghodey aur aslaha khareedney mein kharch farma detey they."
4146,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham bheja jabkey wo un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key khaibar ke sadqe aur khums sey apni virasat talab karti thin. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : hamarey tarkey mein virasat nahin chalti.
4147,"Hazrat Ata sey Allah Taala key farman : (وَ اعْلَمُوْٓا اَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِّنْ شَیْئٍ … الآیۃ),''tum jaan lo ke jo bhi tum ghanimat hasil karo, us ka paanchwan hissa Allah taalaa, uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur rishtey-daaron key liye hai.'' key barey mein marwi hai ke Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka hissa eik hi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us hissey mein sey (muflis aur tang dast logon ko jihad key liye) sawariyan mohaiyya kartey aur is mein sey zarurat mandon aur mohtajon ko detey. jahan chahtey kharch farmatey aur us sey jo chahtey kartey."
4148,"Hazrat Qais bin Muslim sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Hasan bin Muhammad sey Allah Taala key farman : (وَ اعْلَمُوْٓا اَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِّنْ شَیْئٍ فَاَنَّ لِلّٰہِ خُمُسَہٗ),""jaan lo ke tum jo bhi ghanimat hasil karo, us ka khums Allah Taala key liye hai.'' key (mafhoom key) barey mein puchha. unhoney farmaya : ye Allah Taala ka aaghaze-kalam ka andaz hai warna duniya aur aakhirat sab Allah Taala hi key liye hain, albatta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad aap aur qurbat-daaron key do hisson mein logon ney ikhtilaf kiya. baaz ney kaha ke aap key baad aap ka hissa khalifa aur haakime-waqt key liye hoga. isi tarah baaz ney kaha ke rishtey-daaron ka hissa ab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehale-bait key liye hai. aur baaz ney kaha : ab rishtey-daaron ka hissa khalifae-waqt key rishtey-daaron key liye hoga, phir bil-aakhir unhoney is baat par ittifaq kar liya ke ye dono hissey jihad key liye ghodey aur aslaha khareedney mein kharch kiye jaeyn, chunanche hazraat Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-khilaafat mein ye dono hissey isi musraf mein kharch hotey rahey."
4149,"Musa bin Abu Aaysha sey riwayat hai ke mainey Yahya bin Jazaar sey is aayat : (وَ اعْلَمُوْٓا اَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِّنْ شَیْئٍ فَاَنَّ لِلّٰہِ خُمُسَہٗ وَ لِلرَّسُوْلِ),  ''tum jaan lo ke jo bhi tum ghanimat hasil karo, us ka paanchwan hissa Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye hai.'' key (mafhoom key) key barey mein puchha. mainey kaha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka khums mein kitna hissa tha? unhoney kaha : khums ka paanchwan hissa."
4150,"Hazrat Mutrif sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Shaabi sey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hissey aur aap key khas hissey key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka (aam) hissa to eik aam musalman aadmi key hissey key barabar tha, albatta (Safee) (khususi hissey) key barey mein aap ko ikhtiyar tha ke jo bhi pasandida aur pakiza chiz aap pasand farmatey ley saktey they."
4151,"Hazrat Yazid bin Shikhkhir sey marwi hai ke main (Basra key mohall ) Mirbad mein Hazrat Mutrif key sath tha ke eik aadmi aaya. uskey paas surkh chamdey ka eik tukda tha. us ney kaha : ye mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney likh kar diya tha. tum mein sey koi padh sakta hai? mainey kaha : main padh deta hun. is mein likha tha : ye dastawez Nabi Akram Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey banu Zuhair bin Uqaish key liye likhi gaee hai ke agar woh (لا الہ الا اللہ محمد رسول اللہ) ki gawahi den, mushrekin sey alag thalag ho jaeyn aur apni hasil karda ghaneematon mein sey khums (hukoomat ko) deney ka iqrar keren, isi ke sath wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka aam hissa aur khususi hissa (Safee) bhi ada karen to (woh be-khof ho kar rahen). in ko Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey aman ka parwana hasil hoga."
4152,"Hazrat Mujahid bayan kartey hain ke wo khums jo Allah Taala key liye aur uskey Rasool key liye tha, wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key rishtey-daaron key liye tha kyonkey wo sadqa nahin letey they lihaza khums ka paanchwan hissa Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye tha. aur khums ka eik aur paanchwan hissa aap key rishtey-daaron key liye tha. yatimon key liye bhi isi qadr (paanchwan hissa) tha. miskinon key liye bhi (paanchwan hissa) tha. aur musafiron key liye bhi paanchwan hissa tha. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) bayan kartey hain ke Allah Taala ney farmaya : (وَاعْلَمُوا أَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِنْ شَيْءٍ فَأَنَّ لِلَّهِ خُمُسَهُ وَلِلرَّسُولِ وَلِذِي الْقُرْبَى وَالْيَتَامَى وَالْمَسَاكِينِ وَابْنِ السَّبِيلِ),''tum jaan lo ke jo bhi tum ghanimat hasil karo, us ka paanchwan hissa Allah Taala uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), aap key rishtey daaron, yatimon, miskinon aur musafiron key liye hai.''Allah taala ka farmana (Allah) ye to aaghaze-kalam (tabarruk) key liye hai. kyonkey sab cheezen Allah Taala hi ki hain. mumkin hai Allah Taala ney ghanimat aur khums key masley mein apna zikr pehley is liye farmaya ho ke ye intehai umda kamai hai. Allah Taala ney sadqey ki nisbat apni taraf nahin farmaee kyonkey ye logon ka mail kuchail hai. ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke ghanimat sey kuchh maal ley kar Baitullah par kharch kiya jaeyga aur ye Allah Taala wala hissa hai. aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka hissa ab waqt ke Imam, yani Haakime Aa'laa ko milega. wo us sey ghodey aur aslaha waghera khareedega aur jin ko wo munasib samjhey, in ko is mein sey atiyaat dega, maslan : jin logon ney musalmanon key liye koi karnaamey sar-anjaam diye hon aur jin sey musalmanon ka faeyda ho. muhaddeseen, fuqaha huffaz aur deegar ehale-ilm waghera (bhi is mein shamil hain). qurbat-daari ka hissa banu Haashim aur banu Muttalib mein taqseem hoga, chahey wo maaldaar hon ya faqir. ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke un mein sey sirf fuqaraa ko milega, maaldaron ko nahin, jaisey yatimon aur musafiron mein sey sirf fuqaraa ko milta hai. aur merey nazdik ye qol ziyada durust hai. (وااللہ اعلم). chhotey badey, mard aur aurat sab is mein barabar hongey kyonkey Allah Taala ney ye hissa unkey liye muqarrar farma diya hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un mein taqseem farmaya. kisi hadees mein ye zikr nahi key aap ney un mein sey kisi ko dusrey sey ziyada diya ho. (us ki daleel ye hai ke) agar koi shakhs kisi khandan key liye apni chhuti hui jaaidaad key teesrey hissey ki wasiyat kar jaey to ulamaaon mein koi ikhtilaf nahin ke wo unkey darmiyan barabar taqseem hoga. muzakkir, muannas (mard aur aurat) ginti key waqt eik sey hongey (yani kam aur ziyada nahin diya jaeyga). isi tarah jo bhi chiz kisi qabiley ko di jaey, wo un mein barabar taqseem hoti hai siwaye iske ke wazahat kar di jaey aur Allah Taala hi tofiq deney wala hai. aur yatimon, miskinon aur musafiron key hissey un mein sey musalmanon ko milengey (kafiron ko nahin). aur in mein sey kisi ko do hissey nahin diye jaeyngey, maslan : miskeen ka bhi, musafir ka bhi (balke eik hissa diya jaeyga) usey kaha jaeyga. in mein sey jaunsa chaho ley lo. aur baqi chaar hissey (yani khums key ilawa ghanimat) Imame-waqt (Haakime-Aa'laa ya us ka numaainda) jang mein hazir honey waley baligh musalmanon mein taqseem kar dega."
4153,"Hazrat Malik bin Aus bin Hadsan sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Abbas Raziallahu anhuma Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jhagadtey huye aaye. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : merey aur is (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) key darmiyan faisla farmaiye. haazirin ney bhi kaha : inkey darmiyan zarur faisla farmaiye. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : lekin main inkey darmiyan faisla nahin karunga jabkey inhein ilm hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : hamari virasat taqseem nahin hoti. jo kuchh hum chhod jaeyn, wo sadqa hota hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) un (mutnaze (jhagdewali)) zaminon key sarparast aur mutawalli they. aap un sey apney ehale-bait ki khurak letey aur baqi aamdani baitul maal mein rakhtey they. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap key baad unkey sarparast aur mutawalli baney. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key baad main unka sarparast aur mutawalli bana aur mainey un mein wohi kuchh kiya jo kuchh wo kiya kartey they, phir ye dono (hazaraat Ali aur Abbas Raziallahu anhuma) merey paas aaye aur mujh sey mutalba kiya ke ye zamin unkey supurd ki jaey is shart par ke wo usi tareeqey sey us ka intizam kerengey jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kartey they, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) kartey they aur main karta raha hun. mainey us shart par in ko zamin dey di aur in sey ehad aur paiman ley liya. phir ye dobara merey paas aaye. ye (Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey they ke itni zamin merey intizam mein dey dijiye jo mujhey merey bhatijey (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bator virasat milti. aur ye (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey they ke itni zamin merey intizam mein dey dijiye jo meri biwi (Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha)) ko virasat mein milti. agar to ye chahen ke main in ko is shart par zamin supurd kar dun ke wo is mein is tarah intizam karen jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kartey they, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) kartey they aur main karta raha hun, phir to main is shart par zamin unkey supurd karta hun, warna main intizam sanbhaal leta hun, phir aap ney ye aayat padhi. ( وَاعْلَمُوا أَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِنْ شَيْءٍ . . . . . ),''tum jaan lo ke jo bhi tum ghanimat hasil karo us ka paanchwan hissa Allah taalaa, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), rishtey daaron (eahle-bait), yatimon, miskinon aur musafiron key liye hai.'' khums to unkey liye ho gaya. ( اِنَّمَا الصَّدَقتُ لِلْفُقَرَآءِ وَ الْمَسَکِیْنِ ),''bilashuba sadqaat fuqaraa, miskinon, sadqaat jama karney waley mulazimon ke dilon ko narm karne ke liye, ghulamon , qarzdaaron aur mujahideen key liye hain, ye (sadqaat) inkey liye ho gaey.'' ( وَمَا اَفَاءَ اللہُ عَلیٰ رَسُوْلِہِ مِنْھُمْ . . . . . ),''aur jo maale-ghanimat Allah Taala ney apney Rasool karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko un sey (bano Nazeer) sey ata farmaya hai, uskey liye tum ney na ghodey dodaye na oont.'' Hazrat Zohri bayan kartey hain ke ye zameenein khalis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye thin. isi tarah kuchh Arbi bastiyan jaisey fidak waghera bhi aap key liye khas thin. jo kuchh Allah Taala ney apney Rasool Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko un bastiyon sey diya hai, wo Allah taalaa, uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ehale-bait, yatimon, miskinon aur musafiron key liye hai. ye un fuqaraa muhajrin key liye hai jin ko unkey ghar-baar sey nikal diya gaya aur un ansaar key liye jo Daarul-Islam (Madina Munawwara) key rehney waley hain aur muhajrin ki aamad sey qabl hi musalman ho chukey they aur un logon key liye bhi jo unkey baad aaye (ya ayengey). ye aayat tamam musalmanon ko shamil hai. kisi musalman ko bhi bahar nahin rehney diya. sab ka is maal mein haq hai, albatta wo ghulam jo tumhari milkiyat mein hain (unka koi haq nahin). aur agar main zinda raha to Insha-Allah har musalman ko us ka haq laziman mil key rahega."
